38.
 As the Miri folds
 Coming untouched yet again
 A sight breathtaking 
 
 
 40.
 The Caelo comes now
 Showing the guaranteed way
 Blinking and Shining
 
 
 45.
 The rain cleared the field
 Creating a serene mood
 Silence encasing
 
 
 51.
 The blue skies with clouds
 Rain waters from the heavens
 Shadowing below
 
 
 46.
 One born of the sun
 Another born of the moon
 Power infinite
 
 
 42.
 What holds the lune at bay
 When the mornings sun not come
 And what comes known not
 
 
 27.
 As the hummingbirds sing
 And the weeping willows cry
 Spring brings rain and shine
 
 
 25.
 As the flower falls
 Trees breath a breath of relief
 Free of the burden
 
 
 21.
 The morning brings sun
 That grows and gives glowing light
 Heading all who see
 
 So, they're not in order, and they are the ones that I like the best... But, if you could tell me the number of your favorite one, and maybe tell me what I could do to make them better, I would appreciate it!
